    public class EventProcessedByEventTokenMatcher
extends org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.api.impl.BaseMatcher<EventProcessedByEventTokenMatch>
    Generated pattern matcher API of the org.eclipse.viatra.cep.core.engine.runtime.eventProcessedByEventToken pattern, providing pattern-specific query methods.

    Use the pattern matcher on a given model via on(ViatraQueryEngine), e.g. in conjunction with ViatraQueryEngine#on(Notifier).

    Matches of the pattern will be represented as EventProcessedByEventTokenMatch.

    Original source: 

     pattern eventProcessedByEventToken(event : Event, eventToken : EventToken) {
        EventToken.lastProcessed(eventToken, event);
 }
